ies- around?utm_source=rss_feed</guid><link/> https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/education/article/3220905/hong-kong-primary-four-pupils-take-third-spot-reading-survey-57-countries-and-territories- around?utm_source=rss_feed<author><![CDATA[Sue Ng]]></author><category>消息</category><category>香港</category><category>香港的教育</category><category>教育</category><category>香港</category><category>冠状病毒大流行</category><category>冠状病毒大流行：所有故事</category><category>香港冠状病毒</category><category>新加坡</category><category>香港小四学生在全球57个国家和地区的阅读调查中名列第三</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Beijing tightens control over rural China with training campaign for thousands of village chiefs]]></title><description><![CDATA[<p>数以万计的中国村党委书记参加了由执政的共产党最高人事部门和中央党校主办的第一次国家级<a href="https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3210183/china-says-its-plan-bring-modern-socialism-rural-areas-cant-afford-fail-external-pressures-mount?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220883_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="87b20ab9-2064-459d-8ba4-9c1b730f8947" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">培训班</a>——这是加强北京对<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3220690/chinas-new-rural-law-force-accused-bullying-farmers-after-videos-overreach-raise-concern-about?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220883_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="706c3f0a-6ef2-4f4a-8b32-bf5cfe7edbfa" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">农村治理</a>控制的大规模运动的一部分。</p><p>辅导班的规模对于北京的<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3098179/chinas-communist-party-school-told-ensure-loyalty-after?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220883_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="1faa1832-e2c2-11ea-8e8d-92e5de2d33e5" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">中央党校</a>来说是不寻常的，它通常侧重于培训至少在县级担任部门负责人职位的有前途的党员干部，为他们在政府中的晋升做准备。下级官员通常在各自的省级或市级党校支部接受培训。 </p><div class="meter