aining-campaign-thousands-village-chiefs?utm_source=rss_feed</guid><link/> https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3220883/beijing-tightens-control-over-rural-china-training-campaign-thousands-village-chiefs?utm_source=rss_feed<author><![CDATA[William Zheng]]></author><category>消息</category><category>中国</category><category>共产党政治</category><category>北京通过对数千名村长的培训活动加强对中国农村的控制</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Hong Kong’s treasury chief stonewalls calls for more relief measures for homebuyers as Legco approves stamp duty bill]]></title><description><![CDATA[<p>随着立法者批准了一项针对廉价房屋买家的减税法案，香港财政部长对采取更多救济措施以帮助居民购买房产的呼吁进行了阻挠。</p><p>财经事务及库务局局长许清宇周三表示，该法案将通过减少高达 67,500 港元（8,612 美元）的印花税付款，使约 37,000 名购房者受益。 </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" x=".75" y="9.75"></rect><path d="m3.75 9.75v-3.75c0-2.89949494 2.35050506-5.25 5.25-5.25 2.8994949 0 5.25 2.35050506 5.25 5.25v3.75"></path><path d="m9.00000067 15.75c-.20710745 0-.37500067.1678932-.37500067.3749993 0 .2071075.16789322.3750007.37500067.3750007.20710611 0 .37499933-.1678932.37499933-.3750007.0002665-.0995369-.03915673-.1950746-.10954072-.2654586-.070384-.070384-.16592164-.1098072-.26545861-.1095407z"></path></g></svg></div></div><div class="dm__b center-block"><div><div class="dm__h mb-16">您已达到免费文章数量限制。</div><div class="dm__t center-block">订阅 SCMP 以无限制地访问我们屡获殊荣的新闻</div><div class="dm__s2 mt-30"><div class="dm__sb" id="subscribe-btn-11-large" role="button" tabindex="0" subscriptions-action="subscribe" subscriptions-service="subscribe.google.com" subscriptions-